name: Attrecto Innovations Corp
tag_list: mobile, smartphone, ios, android, windows-phone, development
overview:
Attrecto Innovations Corp. is a mobile-maniac smartphone app-developer team.

Their mission is to develop creative and professional smartphone applications (Android, iOS, Windows Phone) that are practical and at the same time well-designed.

Their clients can enjoy the benefit of our experience not only during the application development but also in the brainstorming phase, where their marketing and sales professionals help proactively in the specification design.

They develop smartphone applications and provide solutions not only for their clients, but they also develop and publish their own apps, utilizing their world-class innovative ideas.
